reviewText: I'm a big Tracey Gold fan & I've seen a lot of her movies. This one is a winner. She plays a drug addict who gets amnesia & can't remember her former life. For anyone who loves Tracey Gold I definitely rcommend seeing it. Some of her other good movies are "For the Love of Nancy", & "Midwest Obsession". Plus many more. For information about Tracey go to my website, "Wonderful TraceyGold."
